    "body": "Here is an example that I made.\r\n\r\n```TOML\r\n[custom.uv]\r\ncommand = 'cat .python-version'\r\ndetect_files = ['uv.lock']\r\nsymbol = 'UV '\r\nstyle = 'bold bright-red'\r\n````\r\n\r\nInstead of `UV` as the symbol I actually use the floppy nerdfont symbol. Just remember to have a space after the ico in the string. Otherwise it displays small.\r\n",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
