    "body": "I'm doing this right now, which also works:\n\n```toml\n[python]\npython_binary = \"_starship_python.sh\"\n```\n\n```bash\n# ~/.local/bin/_starship_python.sh\n\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\n$(uv python find) \"$@\"\n```\n\nI wouldn't recommend using `uv run python`, because this will try to setup the venv if it doesn't exist yet. With `uv python find`, this will not happen.",
