    "updated_at": "2025-06-24T20:25:55Z",
    "body": "This is the custom module I'm using to only display my `uv` python for a given project:\n\n```toml\n[custom.uv_python]\ncommand = 'uv python find --show-version'\ndetect_files = ['.python-version', 'pyproject.toml', 'uv.lock']\nsymbol = \"<nerdfont symbol>\"\nstyle = \"<colors>\"\nformat = '[ $symbol( $output) ]($style)'\n```",
