    "body": "Thanks for sharing! I modified it a bit with the defaults from the builtin python extension.\n\n```toml\n[custom.uv_python]\ncommand = 'uv python find --show-version'\nformat = 'via [${symbol}(${output} )]($style)'\nsymbol = \"uv \"\ndetect_extensions = ['py', 'ipynb']\ndetect_files = ['.python-version', 'Pipfile', '__init__.py', 'pyproject.toml', 'requirements.txt', 'setup.py', 'tox.ini', 'uv.lock', 'pylock.toml']\nstyle = \"bold purple\"\n```",
